short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Colorful Rubik's Cube in your browser from tCubed!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Play the most beautiful Rubik's Cube Chrome extension now! Very Quick launch into a popup without redirecting to a website.

Rotate the cube, rows, and columns by clicking or draging!

Can't solve it in one sitting? No worries! Automatic Save and Restore :)

You will be sure to love the attractively colored Rubik's Cube and fun sounds :) Or, mute the effects if you prefer.

One-click to show the computer solving the puzzle.

Automatically tracks your total moves and solved puzzles.

More at http://www.PlaytCubed.com/games/rubiks-cube
